{"tid":1423042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：如主流意見認為我無法勝任特首　我會辭職","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:47:10.000Z","uid":235391,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d314f68a7b22bfb7a9a950b925c0103e5647c7a2","tid":1423042,"uid":235391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/467993/org/34197338ddee25bdd6d3da1a536f19c4.png/vosLt9dfepkzcusuI6PBzZpiqWkx4Tcy1lP4PtZT-D4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F467993%2Forg%2F34197338ddee25bdd6d3da1a536f19c4.png%2FvosLt9dfepkzcusuI6PBzZpiqWkx4Tcy1lP4PtZT-D4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=9afcf324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有觀眾問林鄭月娥是否信任香港人，若她當選後所提出的意見與主流意見不同，會如何處理？林鄭說：「如果香港人的的主流意見認為我無辦法擔任行政長官，我係會辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者朋友一定要不停追問佢 兌現呢個承諾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba004ff167d41c5434505d8402766e8e4202b896","tid":1423042,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"你圍賓賓府可能仲有用"},{"pid":"98d721a2028680594a1128d6fa11433181e8e8fb","tid":1423042,"uid":235391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba004ff167d41c5434505d8402766e8e4202b896","tid":1423042,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"你圍賓賓府可能仲有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"多一個位攻擊佢 <br />\n無信用可言"}]}